ase"><span class="strut" style="height:0.84444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.77777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.072772em;vertical-align:-0.258664em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.441336em;margin-left:-0.02778em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.258664em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，则<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="bold-italic">f</mi><mi>i</mi></msup><mo>∈</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="double-struck">R</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>N</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>N</mi><mi>z</mi><mi>i</mi></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\bm{f}^i \in \mathbb{R}^{(N_x^i + N_z^i) \times d_i}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.1034439999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord boldsymbol" style="margin-right:0.11042em;">f</span></span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9090039999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.1473400000000002em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9944599999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbb">R</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9944599999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9020857142857143em;"><span style="top:-2.214em;margin-left:-0.10903em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">x</span></span></span><span style="top:-2.931em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9020857142857143em;"><span style="top:-2.214em;margin-left:-0.10903em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span></span></span><span style="top:-2.931em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span><span class="mbin mtight">×</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3280857142857143em;"><span style="top:-2.357em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.143em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，该向量会被作为transformer的输入。</p><h4 id="cyclic-shifting-strategy"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#cyclic-shifting-strategy"></a> Cyclic Shifting strategy</h4><p>直接对window sequence计算attention存在两个问题：</p><ol><li><p>attention map的大小相比于pixel-to-pixel来说小很多，得到的是粗糙的相似度得分；</p></li><li><p>由于不同head使用的窗口大小不同，因此不同head得到的输出大小也是不同的。</p></li></ol><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Cyclic_shifting.png" alt="循环移位策略示意图"></p><p>为了解决这两个问题，作者使用了上图所示的循环移位策略：定义移位操作<code>shift(x, y)</code>表示在水平方向上平移x个像素，在垂直方向上平移y个像素；那么对于每个窗口来说，一共有<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>r</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(2r-1)^{2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose"><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>种不同的移位结果（<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>∈</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x, y \in [-r+1, r-1]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7335400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span>各有<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>r</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">2r-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>种选择），这样就能够产生更多的窗口来得到更精细的相似度图。但这样只能解决上述第一个问题，如何使每个head输出大小是一致的在下面会讲到。</p><h3 id="efficient-computation"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#efficient-computation"></a> Efficient Computation</h3><h4 id="spatially-regularized-attention-mask"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#spatially-regularized-attention-mask"></a> Spatially regularized attention mask</h4><p>由于循环移位产生的边界效应，靠近边缘处的样本有更大的概率会破坏目标的整体性和位置信息，因此作者使用了下图所示的空间正则化给这些边缘处的样本更低的权重。</p><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Spatial_Regularization.png" alt="空间正则化"></p><h4 id="computational-optimization"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#computational-optimization"></a> Computational optimization</h4><p>循环移位策略会引入大量的额外计算，作者使用了如下方法降低计算量：</p><ul><li><p>不对<code>Query</code>做循环移位，只对<code>Key</code>和<code>Value</code>做循环移位。</p></li><li><p>消除循环移位产生的重复结果（例如向左移动<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span></span></span></span>距离和向右移动<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r-m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span></span></span></span>距离得到的结果实际上是一样的）。这样第<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span>个head种每个窗口循环移位产生的样本数就是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r_i^2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.072772em;vertical-align:-0.258664em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.441336em;margin-left:-0.02778em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.258664em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，得到的attention map大小为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>×</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>N</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi>N</mi><mi>z</mi><mi>i</mi></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">r_i^2 \times (N_x^i + N_z^i)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.072772em;vertical-align:-0.258664em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.441336em;margin-left:-0.02778em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.258664em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0746639999999998em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.824664em;"><span style="top:-2.4530000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10903em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">x</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.247em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0746639999999998em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.824664em;"><span style="top:-2.4530000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10903em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.247em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，保证了每个head的输出大小是一致的。</p></li><li><p>利用矩阵坐标的排列实现矩阵的循环移位（编程技巧）。</p></li></ul><h2 id="experiments"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#experiments"></a> Experiments</h2><h3 id="results"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#results"></a> Results</h3><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Results1.png" alt="在UAV,LaSOT,TrackingNet,GOT-10k上的实验结果"></p><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Results2.png" alt="在VOT2020上的实验结果"></p><h3 id="ablation-study"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#ablation-study"></a> Ablation Study</h3><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Ablation1.png" alt="各组件效果分析"></p><p>从第二行可以看出由于计算的attention map比较粗糙，直接使用window attention会带来性能的大幅下降，而第三行添加了循环移位后可以很好的解决这一问题。</p><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Ablation2.png" alt="窗口大小分析"></p><p><img src="/project/project/2022/06/30/%E3%80%90CVPR2022%E3%80%91Transformer-Tracking-with-Cyclic-Shifting-Window-Attention/Ablation3.png" alt="运行速度分析"></p><p>经过优化后速度提升了到了<strong>14.9FPS</strong>，作者是在Tesla T4上测试的，不知道在2080Ti上能跑到什么速度。</p><h2 id="参考"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#参考"></a> 参考</h2><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>Swin-Transformer <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.14030">https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.14030</a><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li><li><span id="fn:2" class="footnote-text"><span>STARK <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.17154">https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.17154</a><a href="#fnref:2" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
